  <brief_title>Evaluation of the Beneficial Effects of a Probiotic Product in Healthy Adult Subjects.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Beneficial Effects of a Probiotic Product (Lactoflorene Plus) in Healthy Adult Subjects in Particular Psychological Stress Conditions.</official_title>
