  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled, cross-over trial performed at one centre in
      Italy to explore the ability of a multistrain probiotic mixture, to modulate markers of
      inflammation and intestinal barrier function and gastrointestinal symptoms in healthy
      volunteers with self-reported anxiety.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
